name: Squid the Whale/The Composure/Attalus tickets
description:
Buy a ticket. Then, send an email to thatgirlinterviews@gmail.com with your name(and friends names if they were bought at once) and purchase number. This is an EARLY show, we are starting with Attalus at 7pm and everything will be over by 9pm. 

PRESALE TICKETS ARE A MUST!! 

The day before the show the address of the venue will be emailed to you(it will be in Raleigh).  Make sure you have photo identification day of the show since it will be checked at the door. 

No alcohol will be served on premises and no one underage will be admitted inside if suspected of being under the influence. 
Tickets are refundable only at the seller's discretion.




The Composure: www.facebook.com/TheComposureRock
Squid The Whale: www.facebook.com/squidthewhale
Attalus: www.facebook.com/AttalusMusic
